Package com.guardsquare.dexguard.runtime.detection

Class RootDetectorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.content.Context
      • android.content.ContextWrapper
        • android.app.Service
          • com.guardsquare.dexguard.runtime.detection.RootDetectorService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.content.ComponentCallbacks2
    public class RootDetectorService
extends android.app.Service
    This class implements the Magisk-related checks as a service that is run in an isolated process. We use this approach to address the concern that the latest versions of Magisk can hide itself from the main process of an application and from all processes that are forked from it. See DGD-3274.
